{"$category":"crawled","mainimg":"http://file28.mafengwo.net/M00/6B/09/wKgB6lS-HwGAVrcFAAnIO5n3hDI30.book.w230.jpeg","addname":"武当山","tags":"<span>道教</span>\n                    <span>隐士</span>\n                    <span>武侠</span>\n                    <span>太极</span>\n                    <span>古建</span>\n                    <span>名山</span>\n                <div class=\"clear\"></div>","abstracts":"<p><strong>简介</strong> 说起武当山，总是充满着传奇色彩，正如千百年来无数在此隐居修道者一样，它仿佛永远隐匿在厚重层叠的烟云之中，时隐时现。武当山古名太和山，是我国著名的道教圣地之一，不仅拥有奇特绚丽的自然景观，而且拥有丰富多彩的人文景观。从传说中的真武大帝到武侠小说中的太极张三丰，从汉魏时期的的孙思邈、吕洞宾到宋元时期的叶希真、刘道明，因为武当山的独特环境，它一直备受隐居者青睐。自古以来，武当山便是道家追求仙境的理想之地，历代都没停止过在武当山上营建宫殿庙宇，明成祖朱棣更是以紫禁城的规格来营造大小宫殿，武当山也在此时达到历史的最高峰，现存很多建筑都与那时修建。</p>","imgs":"<li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"0\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file28.mafengwo.net/M00/6B/09/wKgB6lS-HwGAVrcFAAnIO5n3hDI30.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"1\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file28.mafengwo.net/M00/6B/09/wKgB6lS-HwGATtf1AA1hSsUpgRg62.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"2\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file28.mafengwo.net/M00/6B/09/wKgB6lS-HwGADL-_AAyyBaePziU80.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n          